{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01KvriQCAu4rvEt9XwcyHC5r","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I can see the issues clearly:\n\n1. On `/app` vhost:\n   - `ops-user` has full `.*` permissions (should NOT be here at all)\n   - `app-user` has empty `configure` permission (should be `.*`) but has write/read correctly\n\n2. On `/ops` vhost:\n   - `ops-user` has NO permissions at all (should have full `.*` configure/write/read)\n   - `app-user` has no permissions on `/ops` - this is correct\n\nSo I need to:\n1. Fix `app-user` on `/app`: set configure to `.*` (currently empty)\n2. Remove `ops-user` from `/app` entirely\n3. Grant `ops-user` full permissions on `/ops`\n4. Confirm `app-user` stays locked out of `/ops`\n\nI should also look at what the client deployments are actually connecting to and which credentials they're using.","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":801,"cache_read_input_tokens":28793,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":801},"output_tokens":35,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"5d8e28b3-9e6b-4f19-a633-f2fed2b9ef8e","uuid":"0f04d4cf-1343-4be2-a4fc-48628b9f699a","request_id":"req_011Ccdcosx5HHra9zzxz7ZnL"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01KvriQCAu4rvEt9XwcyHC5r","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The issues are clear:\n- `/app`: `app-user` has empty configure (should be `.*`), and `ops-user` is wrongly present\n- `/ops`: `ops-user` has no permissions at all (should have full `.*`)\n\nLet me fix all of this:"}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":801,"cache_read_input_tokens":28793,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":801},"output_tokens":35,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"5d8e28b3-9e6b-4f19-a633-f2fed2b9ef8e","uuid":"1bbc6f8a-de55-4aa7-acc8-29ae5014ec88","request_id":"req_011Ccdcosx5HHra9zzxz7ZnL"}
